CROSSBONES_UNLOCK.m_description: Ultimus has double-crossed Crossbones. Help Crossbones get payback, and in exchange he'll join your S.T.R.I.K.E. team.

Groot has gone missing. Help Rocket track down Groot's whereabouts.
Ultron has taken Groot and stands in Rocket's way. Take him out.
Rocket finds out that Groot is sick. Fight through Ultron's army to take him back.
Protect Groot from Korath and the Kree.
Ronan and the Kree are determined to take out Groot to prevent an intergalactic outbreak.
Nebula and her death squad arrive and will stop at nothing to eliminate Groot.
A.I.M. arrives and intends to take Groot so they can weaponize his fungus for their own purposes.
Scientist Supreme has taken Groot to her space station orbiting planet Klyntar. Save Groot before it's too late.
After getting Groot back, Rocket and the S.T.R.I.K.E. team must break into the A.I.M. lab housing the cure.
Help Rocket and Groot defeat Scientist Supreme once and for all and escape the space station!

ROCKETRACCOON_UNLOCK.m_description: Groot has gone missing! Help Rocket Raccoon save his uprooted friend and in return he'll join your S.T.R.I.K.E. force.

m_missionList.m_description: The S.T.R.I.K.E. team must attempt to lure Thanos out of New York City.
Work with Thanos to escape from the Kree prison ship.
After crash landing on a remote planet in a fallen dimension, Thanos and the S.T.R.I.K.E. team must find a way home.
Thanos and the S.T.R.I.K.E. team must fight their way to a Ravager ship.
Thanos and one member of the S.T.R.I.K.E. team challenge corrupted Yondu and Star-Lord for their ship.
Thanos and the team penetrate the defenses of the multiphasic tetraplex scanner facility.
Thanos and the S.T.R.I.K.E. team encounter a corrupted Thor and Loki while fighting their way to the scanner.
A corrupted Iron Man and the Guardians of the Galaxy stand in the way of the S.T.R.I.K.E. team and the scanner control capsule.
The team must protect Gamora and defeat a corrupted Nebula while Thanos searches for the Reality Stone in the control capsule.
The S.T.R.I.K.E. team must fight off corrupted Thanos and Ultimus's army.

THANOS_EVENT.m_description: Thanos and the STRIKE team are trapped in an alternate dimension and must find their way back home!

m_missionList.m_description: Deadpool seeks revenge for Ultimus destroying his favorite chimichanga restaurant.
The mercs are not happy that Deadpool is getting in their way. Bullseye aims (WINK WINK) to get back at him.
Wolverine seeks to take control of the Deadpool situation.
Deadpool and Wolverine search for Cable who has been captured by Ultimus.
Save Cable from corrupted Spider-Man and his cronies.
With help from Cable and Deadpool, break into the facility that houses the corrupted Techno-Organic Virus.
Deadpool and Cable encounter corrupted Thanos guarding the corrupted Techno Virus supply.
Fight off an angry mob of minions!
Stop Scientist Supreme and Ultron from generating a new batch of the corrupted Techno-Organic Virus.
Take out corrupted Vision before his Ultron Operators can create a new batch of the Techno Virus, and to ensure it can never be recreated.

DEADPOOL_EVENT.m_description: Deadpool must avenge the loss of his favorite chimichanga restaurant at the hands of Ultimus.
